var orderToForce = 6;
// Categorias a forzar nuestro orden
categories = ['cat50702','cat1041032','cat50834','cat1041034','cat1041036','cat7630942','cat50703','cat50568','cat1091142','cat1091146','cat1091150','cat3011048','cat50568','cat50846','cat50846','cat50478','cat1660941','cat770967','cat770969','cat1071043','cat701459','cat770971','cat271051','cat50888','cat50624'];

// Se ejecuta luego de cada click del usuario
function callback(e) {
    var e = window.e || e;
    

    // Si click NO fue hecho sobre un tag &lt;a&gt;, retornar
    if (e.target.tagName === 'A'){
        elem = e.target;
   } else{
        return;
    }
///    // Caso de boton 'Ver Todo' en https://www.falabella.com/falabella-cl/category/cat2008/Mundo-Bebe
///    else if (e.target.parentElement.tagName === 'A')
///        elem = e.target.parentElement;


    // Si existe .href continuamos
    if (elem.href) {
        var url = elem.href;

        // ((Check URL))
        // Reviso si el link contiene alguna de las categorias
        for (var i=0; i &lt; categories.length; i++)
        {
            if (url.indexOf('/'+categories[i]+'/') &gt;= 0) {

                if (url.indexOf('gridView=') &gt;= 0) {
                    newurl = url.replace(/(gridView=\d+)/i,'gridView='+orderToForce);
                } else {
                    if (url.indexOf('?') &gt;= 0)
                        urlchar = '&amp;';
                    else
                        urlchar = '?';
                    newurl = url + urlchar +'gridView='+orderToForce;
                }
                elem.href = newurl;

                break;
            }
        }
    }
}

if (document.addEventListener) {
    document.addEventListener('click', callback, true);
    document.addEventListener('contextmenu', callback, true);
    document.addEventListener('auxclick', callback, true);
}
else
    document.attachEvent('onclick', callback);

      /*Tallas Vans*/

        var $brandHighlightList = $(
          'div[data-module-region="brandHighlightList"]'
        ).find(".fb-pod-group__item.fb-pod-group__item--product");
        $brandHighlightList.each(function(index, el) {
          var fbPodHeaderLink = $(this)
            .find(".fb-pod__header a.fb-pod__header-link")
            .attr("href");
          fbPodHeaderLink = fbPodHeaderLink.split("/");
          var skuLink = fbPodHeaderLink[3];
          var fbPodMedia = $(this)
            .find(".fb-pod__header img.fb-pod__media")
            .attr("src");
          fbPodMedia = fbPodMedia.split("/");
          var skuImg = fbPodMedia[6];
          skuImg = skuImg.split("?");
          skuImg = skuImg[0].split("_");
          $(this)
            .find(".fb-pod__header img.fb-pod__media")
            .attr(
              "src",
              "//falabella.scene7.com/is/image/FalabellaCO/" +
                skuLink +
                "?$PP320x320$"
            );
        });
      }

        jsElement.async = true;
        jsElement.charset = "UTF-8";
        jsElement.src =
          "/static/RDF/site/home/promohuincha/html/scripts/filtros_cocina_menaje.js";
        // finally insert the element to the body element in order to load the script
        document.body.appendChild(jsElement);
      }
      /*fin Filtros ultimas tallas*/

      /*nivel de stock en productos*/
      if (window.location.href.indexOf("/product/") != -1) {
        var pathArray = window.location.pathname.split("/");
        if (window.location.href.indexOf("/product/") != -1) {
          var pathArray = window.location.pathname.split("/");
          if (pathArray[3]) {
            fetch(
              "https://www.falabella.com.co/falabella-co/browse/productJson.jsp?productId=" +
                pathArray[3]
            )
              .then(function(response) {
                return response.json();
              })
              .then(function(data) {
                if (data[0].stockLevel) {
                  console.warn(data[0].stockLevel);
                }
                if (data[0].backEndCategory.startsWith("J11")) {
                  var res = data[0].stockLevel.replace(/{/g, "");
                  res = res.replace(/}/g, "");
                  res = res.split("=");
                  res = parseInt(res[1]);
                  console.log(res);
                }
              })
              .catch(function(error) {
                console.warn(error);
              });
          }
        }
      }
      /*fin nivel de stock en productos*/
    }, 1000);

    /*newsletter*/
    setTimeout(function() {
      var html_footer = document.getElementById("fb-footer__newsletter");
      html_new_footer = `
      &lt;div id="fb-footer__newsletter" class="fb-footer-newsletter__form"&gt;

              &lt;p style="margin-bottom:20px;"&gt;
                  &lt;a class="link_form" href="https://www.falabella.com.co/falabella-co/page/registros_2018?staticPageId=7100001" style="font-size: 15px;"&gt;Suscr\&amp;iacute;bete y ent\&amp;eacute;rate primero de los mejores productos y ofertas&lt;/a&gt;

              &lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;`;
      html_footer.innerHTML = html_new_footer;
    }, 1500);

    /* Redirects top level */
    (function(d) {
      "use strict";

      let redirect = (class_element, url_actual, url_redirect) =&gt; {
        let urls = document.querySelectorAll(class_element);
        for (let index in urls) {
          if (urls[index].href === url_actual) {
            urls[index].href = url_redirect;
          }
        }
      };

      redirect(
        ".js-masthead__child-links__item__link",

    /*Fin Hasta las seis*/

    /*Hasta las Tres*/

    var queryStringHastaLasTres = null;
    var timeHastaLasTres = new Date();
    if (window.location.href.indexOf("/category/") != -1) {
      if (
        timeHastaLasTres.getHours() &gt;= 7 &amp;&amp;
        timeHastaLasTres.getHours() &lt; 17
      ) {
        if (timeHastaLasTres.getDay() &lt;= 5) {
          var startWorkerHastaLasTres = function startWorkerHastaLasTres() {
            if (typeof Worker !== "undefined") {
              if (typeof workerHastalasTres == "undefined") {
                workerHastalasTres = new Worker(
                  "/static/RDF/site/home/promohuincha/html/scripts/worker_flag_hasta_tres.js"
                );
                var arraySkusHastalasTres = [];
                $(".fb-pod__item__compare__input").each(function(index) {
                  arraySkusHastalasTres.push($(this).val());
                });
                console.log("hasta las tres", arraySkusHastalasTres);
                workerHastalasTres.postMessage({ msg: arraySkusHastalasTres });

                workerHastalasTres.onmessage = function(event) {
                  console.log("hasta las tres", event.data);
                  event.data.map(function(index) {
                    var htmlEntregaVenticuadroHoras =
                      '&lt;div class="fb-flag-entrega--en-venticuadro-horas"&gt;Entrega Bogot&amp;aacute; &lt;span&gt;24 Horas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;';
                    var parentSkusDOM = $("#fb-pod__item__input-" + index)
                      .parent()
                      .closest("div");
                    var podItem = parentSkusDOM.parent().closest("div");
                    var sectionPodTop = podItem.find(
                      ".pod-body .section__pod-top"
                    );
                    var existFlagElement = sectionPodTop.find(
                      ".fb-flag-entrega--en-venticuadro-horas"
                    );
                    if (existFlagElement.length === 0) {
                      sectionPodTop.prepend(htmlEntregaVenticuadroHoras);
                    }
                  });
                };

                $(window).scroll(function() {
                  if ($(".fb-pod__item__compare__input").length &gt; 0) {
                    if (queryStringHastaLasTres !== location.search) {
                      queryStringHastaLasTres = location.search;
                      var timeHastaLasTresScroll = new Date();
                      if (
                        timeHastaLasTresScroll.getHours() &gt;= 7 &amp;&amp;
                        timeHastaLasTresScroll.getHours() &lt; 17
                      ) {
                        if (timeHastaLasTresScroll.getDay() &lt;= 5) {
                          if (
                            $(".fb-flag-entrega--en-venticuadro-horas")
                              .length &lt;= 0
                          ) {
                            // not exists
                            var arraySkusHastalasTres = [];
                            $(".fb-pod__item__compare__input").each(function(
                              index
                            ) {
                              arraySkusHastalasTres.push($(this).val());
                            });
                            console.log(
                              "hasta las tres on",
                              arraySkusHastalasTres
                            );
                            workerHastalasTres.postMessage({
                              msg: arraySkusHastalasTres
                            });

                            workerHastalasTres.onmessage = function(event) {
                              console.log("hasta las tres on", event.data);
                              event.data.map(function(index) {
                                var htmlEntregaVenticuadroHoras =
                                  '&lt;div class="fb-flag-entrega--en-venticuadro-horas"&gt;Entrega Bogot&amp;aacute; &lt;span&gt;24 Horas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;';
                                var parentSkusDOM = $(
                                  "#fb-pod__item__input-" + index
                                )
                                  .parent()
                                  .closest("div");
                                var podItem = parentSkusDOM
                                  .parent()
                                  .closest("div");
                                var sectionPodTop = podItem.find(
                                  ".pod-body .section__pod-top"
                                );
                                var existFlagElement = sectionPodTop.find(
                                  ".fb-flag-entrega--en-venticuadro-horas"
                                );
                                if (existFlagElement.length === 0) {
                                  sectionPodTop.prepend(
                                    htmlEntregaVenticuadroHoras
                                  );
                                }
                              });
                            };
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                });
              }
            } else {
              console.log(
                "Sorry, your browser does not support Web Workers..."
              );
            }
          };

          var stopWorkerHastaLasTres = function stopWorkerHastaLasTres() {
            w.terminate();
            w = undefined;
          };

          var workerHastalasTres;

          startWorkerHastaLasTres();

          $(document).ready(function() {
            if (
              window.location.href.indexOf("/category/cat1360967/") != -1 ||
              window.location.href.indexOf("/category/cat790955/") != -1
            ) {
              var htmlStyleHastaLasTres =
                '&lt;div&gt;&lt;style type="text/css"&gt;.fb-flag-entrega--en-venticuadro-horas{right: -141px;top: -180px;}&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/div&gt;';
              $(htmlStyleHastaLasTres).insertAfter(".fb-backdrop");
            }
          });
        }
      }
    }

    if (window.location.href.indexOf("/product/") != -1) {
      $.getScript(
        "/static/RDF/site/home/promohuincha/html/scripts/flag_in_pdp.js",
        function(data, textStatus, jqxhr) {}
      );
    }

    caches.delete("falabellaHighPerformance2");
  });

  /*

     console.log('Service Worker Ready');
  });

</script>
